item.title: 3 Of My 525 & 562 Servers are not running, help please
item.dc:creator: @Lordabyssal Lordabyssal
item.description:
@Lordabyssal wrote:

For me the port is located in server.java

“C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.7.0_13\bin\java.exe” src\net\com\codeusa\Server

try this. if this does not work find your server.java and add dir for it.

Mine is
“C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.7.0_13\bin\java.exe” src\net\com\codeusa\ server.Server

This is mine run.bat

@echo off
title Exilium Server
java -noverify -javaagent:“C:\Program Files (x86)\ZeroTurnaround\JRebel\jrebel.jar” -Xmx800m -cp bin;deps/poi.jar;deps/mysql.jar;deps/mina.jar;deps/slf4j.jar;deps/slf4j-nop.jar;deps/jython.jar;log4j-1.2.15.jar; server.Server
start Run-Server.bat
exit

The -noverify -javaagent:“C:\Program Files (x86)\ZeroTurnaround\JRebel\jrebel.jar” is my own add on.

First server is file second is server.java
